channel.title: Rsps 2015
channel.description:
I started after playing jbirdscape with a own private server. As many others i had a dream making a nice big server. 2009. there was so many nice, and creative servers. I quite for over a year now. But i see no different from 2013 to now. Same server download list. Same copies
If i think back to those day. Of deltascape and allstar. Codes suck as hell but playing was such a great time.
What is left? Is the community getting smaller? Is the end reaching for Rsps?
I'm just very curious :P
